{"tid":1100330,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)LEGO蝙蝠俠 LEGO英雄傳1-2 私刑教育","createTime":"2019-04-10T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T18:44:15.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"022af3a381602b84880f0bcadd925f7dab7310ee","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c7e52665\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=51da6bfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=3ce17061\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Lego_Batman_Movie_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Lego_Batman_Movie_Poster.jpg&h=bb66d29f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/10/The_Lego_Movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F10%2FThe_Lego_Movie_poster.jpg&h=3efbcb27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Equalize_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Equalize_poster.jpg&h=24b407cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.自從結伴拯救了樂高宇宙後，蝙蝠俠則回到高譚市繼續維護正義，而在一場行動中阻止了多年死敵小丑企圖炸毀城市根基後，蝙蝠俠對小丑表示他在他的心目中並不重要，使得小丑在深受打擊下決定對蝙蝠俠進行復仇。行動大獲全勝後過了一天，蝙蝠俠卸下面具以布魯斯&middot;韋恩身份出席了城市冬日派對，而警察局長詹姆士&middot;高登也在派對上卸任後轉交給了其女兒芭芭拉。芭芭拉上任後決定重新修整城市警察系統，也決定不再拜託蝙蝠俠。這時，小丑帶領所有反派闖進派對現場後，卻突然對換裝趕到的蝙蝠俠和芭芭拉舉手投降，並和所有隨行的反派們一起遭逮捕；唯獨只有其戀人哈莉&middot;奎茵逃之夭夭。因為罪惡終結，蝙蝠俠失去了他的影響力..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事於樂高宇宙，所有的人物和建築物都是樂高組成的。故事一開始，維特長老試圖保護一種超級武器「瘋膠魔」（強力膠）以免落入邪惡的企業總裁手中，但企業總裁帶領著部下現身將瘋膠魔奪走，並弄瞎了維特長老的雙眼，得意的總裁正打算離身而去時，長老預言將會有個「非凡」的人會成為救世主來阻止瘋膠魔，說完便被總裁踹到山谷下<br />\n<br />\n3.週二薄餅日事件過後，當年拯救世界的其中兩位英雄&mdash;&mdash;艾密特（克里斯&middot;普瑞特 飾）與露西（伊莉莎白&middot;班克絲 飾）以為終於可以安享人生，於是與其他好友遷移至美國西部，但邪惡的美漢將軍（史蒂芬妮&middot;碧翠絲 飾）率領軍隊入侵世界，露西、蝙蝠俠（威爾&middot;阿奈特 飾）、太空人班尼（查理&middot;戴 飾）等英雄與將軍決戰時更被擄走！為救好友們，艾密特駕駛飛船前往太空，展開營救大行動，卻遇上重重困難，還遇上了鼎鼎大名的雷斯&middot;丹傑維特（克里斯&middot;普瑞特 飾）...... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.名為曾為政府工作的前中情局成員化名為羅柏&middot;麥考現住在麻薩諸塞州的波士頓，並在一間五金賣場上班。他協助他的同事朋友拉爾夫減重，以便通過保安考試。麥考答應已過世的妻子，絕不會再回到過去的危險生活。因妻子生前很愛看書，麥考為了達到讀滿100本書，下班後他習慣帶著一包茶包到住家附近一間餐廳看書，日復一日，過著平靜的生活..<br />\n<br />\n6 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=22346b69\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=940d11d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a981295d313c0ade8f4752e844e9bcd1adbfb8b3","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bef434cc8ddb67d20718f016411809f953318a6","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767ac5fc89e81c64ecce7546ed98f1d5929b9a29","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a2e0bfa9e3638ed5639c714b87e40c4fb9c6c6","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dd1484cf5b1cbcc1a724924d62463c8a11f8de","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c282377662f0e46b776d7fab12fe4713972c1ba5","tid":1100330,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\